        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Sergey', 3: 'It has been several years since Vardim, the executive officer of Kyaranta, banished them here. How do you think the nearly 2,000 commune members survived the Arctic winter?', 4: '1'}"
    },
